Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.

„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£

We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

WE ARE THE MUSKETEERS All for one, one for all! We are the Musketeers, a faction of experienced players dedicated to making money and having fun in the process. We aren't some ragtag bunch of players or a huge gang with terrible organization. We're not just some ordinary faction either. We are a team, working together to make cash and have fun. We believe in hard work and skill. Our ranking system is not based on how many times you suck up to your superiors (like some other factions), but on merit, contribution, and skill. We also believe in learning. As long as you're willing to learn, we have experienced players who can teach you every aspect of the game, and scheduled events and trainings regularly. If you're lacking in skill, don't worry! We'll help you get better. WE ARE THE MUSKETEERS All for one, one for all! We are the Musketeers, a faction of experienced players dedicated to making money and having fun in the process. We aren't some ragtag bunch of players or a huge gang with terrible organization. We're not just some ordinary faction either. We are a team, working together to make cash and have fun. We believe in hard work and skill. Our ranking system is not based on how many times you suck up to your superiors (like some other factions), but on merit, contribution, and skill. We also believe in learning. As long as you're willing to learn, we have experienced players who can teach you every aspect of the game, and scheduled events and trainings regularly. If you're lacking in skill, don't worry! We'll help you get better. What do we offer? - Guidance from experienced players - An active, growing community - Assistance with grinding - An opportunity to rise to the top - Events and Trainings - Frequent Giveaways - Fun and Profit Requirements - Unwavering loyalty to the faction - Be reasonably active (play at least twice a week, minimum) - 13+ (otherwise, why are you even on discord?) - Knowledge of all the game mechanics - Participation and Contribution to the faction - Follow the rules, and respect all faction members - Willingness to learn - No Toxicity APPLY TODAY! „Äé About Us „Äè‚Ö†
Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.
„Äé Benefits „Äè‚Ö°
[+] Assistance with clientele [+] Push for safety and security [+] Friendly environment [+] Benefits from services [+] Giveaways (Workers benefit) [+] Back-up [+] Etc.
„Äé Requirements „Äè‚Ö¢
[-] 3+ Star Horse [-] Respect, discipline and loyalty [-] Devotion to what we stand for [-] Activity on Roblox (TWW) & Discord [-] Common sense [-] Abidance to our Rules [-] Abidance to Discord TOS (Includes 13+) [-] Decent PVP Skills
„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£
We are a PMC, offering our services to anybody who needs it. You can find our shop in the Marketplace server, under the name #paid-protection. Please consider taking a look around, perhaps a service and interest you. We will try our best to reach a deal with you if you seek business, and do our best to provide commissioned members. We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

Misguided Kerbal 10-Jan-22 05:33 AM
WE ARE THE MUSKETEERS All for one, one for all! We are the Musketeers, a faction of experienced players dedicated to making money and having fun in the process. We aren't some ragtag bunch of players or a huge gang with terrible organization. We're not just some ordinary faction either. We are a team, working together to make cash and have fun. We believe in hard work and skill. Our ranking system is not based on how many times you suck up to your superiors (like some other factions), but on merit, contribution, and skill. We also believe in learning. As long as you're willing to learn, we have experienced players who can teach you every aspect of the game, and scheduled events and trainings regularly. If you're lacking in skill, don't worry! We'll help you get better. What do we offer? - Guidance from experienced players - An active, growing community - Assistance with grinding - An opportunity to rise to the top - Events and Trainings - Frequent Giveaways - Fun and Profit Requirements - Unwavering loyalty to the faction - Be reasonably active (play at least twice a week, minimum) - 13+ (otherwise, why are you even on discord?) - Knowledge of all the game mechanics - Participation and Contribution to the faction - Follow the rules, and respect all faction members - Willingness to learn - No Toxicity APPLY TODAY! [ We sell legendary loot, t-logs, and other rare items! Contact us if you're interested in buying! ] https://discord.gg/5pQSA2B6Q9 https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/899476622665728020/905667718634688573/20.png https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/899476622665728020/905667734845657098/21.png https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/899476622665728020/907002948645683240/Poster.png

PIEDMONT TRIBE "at the foot of the mountains." Long ago before any town had been established in the west was the Piedmont Tribe. They hunted, gathered, and wandered peacefully through the land. Then came men from the east with strange machines. They built weird-shaped buildings in the prairie and long railroads with steam engines. The Piedmont tribe still lives while hiding, surviving, and fighting for their tribe, territory, and culture. Founded in the September of 2019, right at the week when the faction update was released, the Piedmont Tribe came into existence. Originally named the Thunder Tribe, they changed to Ponderosa Tribe before deciding on their current name. The name's origins itself come from a history/geography book. In the year 2020, the legacy of the faction began. Great rallies, fun events, as well as Halloween and Christmas update play-throughs were only a tiny portion of what they did during that time. But soon Comanche started attempting to get them to merge, and when they battled with them they lost. Merging into them for a few months as the Bear Clan, they eventually fell into inactivity and disbanded. But now the rebirth of the Piedmont Tribe has begun. Behold our golden age, we will live on! WE ARE THE MUSKETEERS All for one, one for all! We are the Musketeers, a faction of experienced players dedicated to making money and having fun in the process. We aren't some ragtag bunch of players or a huge gang with terrible organization. We're not just some ordinary faction either. We are a team, working together to make cash and have fun. We believe in hard work and skill. Our ranking system is not based on how many times you suck up to your superiors (like some other factions), but on merit, contribution, and skill. We also believe in learning. As long as you're willing to learn, we have experienced players who can teach you every aspect of the game, and scheduled events and trainings regularly. If you're lacking in skill, don't worry! We'll help you get better. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.

We aren't some ragtag bunch of players or a huge gang with terrible organization. We're not just some ordinary faction either. We are a team, working together to make cash and have fun. We believe in hard work and skill. Our ranking system is not based on how many times you suck up to your superiors (like some other factions), but on merit, contribution, and skill. We also believe in learning. As long as you're willing to learn, we have experienced players who can teach you every aspect of the game, and scheduled events and trainings regularly. If you're lacking in skill, don't worry! We'll help you get better. „Äé About Us „Äè‚Ö†
Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.
„Äé Benefits „Äè‚Ö°
[+] Assistance with clientele [+] Push for safety and security [+] Friendly environment [+] Benefits from services [+] Giveaways (Workers benefit) [+] Back-up [+] Etc.
„Äé Requirements „Äè‚Ö¢
[-] 3+ Star Horse [-] Respect, discipline and loyalty [-] Devotion to what we stand for [-] Activity on Roblox (TWW) & Discord [-] Common sense [-] Abidance to our Rules [-] Abidance to Discord TOS (Includes 13+) [-] Decent PVP Skills
„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£
We are a PMC, offering our services to anybody who needs it. You can find our shop in the Marketplace server, under the name #paid-protection. Please consider taking a look around, perhaps a service and interest you. We will try our best to reach a deal with you if you seek business, and do our best to provide commissioned members. We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

„Äé About Us „Äè‚Ö†
Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.
„Äé Benefits „Äè‚Ö°
[+] Assistance with clientele [+] Push for safety and security [+] Friendly environment [+] Benefits from services [+] Giveaways (Workers benefit) [+] Back-up [+] Etc.

„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£
We are a PMC, offering our services to anybody who needs it. You can find our shop in the Marketplace server, under the name #paid-protection. Please consider taking a look around, perhaps a service and interest you. We will try our best to reach a deal with you if you seek business, and do our best to provide commissioned members. We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

„Äé About Us „Äè‚Ö†
Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.
„Äé Benefits „Äè‚Ö°
[+] Assistance with clientele [+] Push for safety and security [+] Friendly environment [+] Benefits from services [+] Giveaways (Workers benefit) [+] Back-up [+] Etc.
„Äé Requirements „Äè‚Ö¢
[-] 3+ Star Horse [-] Respect, discipline and loyalty [-] Devotion to what we stand for [-] Activity on Roblox (TWW) & Discord [-] Common sense [-] Abidance to our Rules [-] Abidance to Discord TOS (Includes 13+) [-] Decent PVP Skills
„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£
We are a PMC, offering our services to anybody who needs it. You can find our shop in the Marketplace server, under the name #paid-protection. Please consider taking a look around, perhaps a service and interest you. We will try our best to reach a deal with you if you seek business, and do our best to provide commissioned members. We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

„Äé About Us „Äè‚Ö†
Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.
„Äé Benefits „Äè‚Ö°
[+] Assistance with clientele [+] Push for safety and security [+] Friendly environment [+] Benefits from services [+] Giveaways (Workers benefit) [+] Back-up [+] Etc.
„Äé Requirements „Äè‚Ö¢
[-] 3+ Star Horse [-] Respect, discipline and loyalty [-] Devotion to what we stand for [-] Activity on Roblox (TWW) & Discord [-] Common sense [-] Abidance to our Rules [-] Abidance to Discord TOS (Includes 13+) [-] Decent PVP Skills
„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£
We are a PMC, offering our services to anybody who needs it. You can find our shop in the Marketplace server, under the name #paid-protection. Please consider taking a look around, perhaps a service and interest you. We will try our best to reach a deal with you if you seek business, and do our best to provide commissioned members. We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

„Äé About Us „Äè‚Ö†
Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.
„Äé Benefits „Äè‚Ö°
[+] Assistance with clientele [+] Push for safety and security [+] Friendly environment [+] Benefits from services [+] Giveaways (Workers benefit) [+] Back-up [+] Etc.
„Äé Requirements „Äè‚Ö¢
[-] 3+ Star Horse [-] Respect, discipline and loyalty [-] Devotion to what we stand for [-] Activity on Roblox (TWW) & Discord [-] Common sense [-] Abidance to our Rules [-] Abidance to Discord TOS (Includes 13+) [-] Decent PVP Skills
„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£
We are a PMC, offering our services to anybody who needs it. You can find our shop in the Marketplace server, under the name #paid-protection. Please consider taking a look around, perhaps a service and interest you. We will try our best to reach a deal with you if you seek business, and do our best to provide commissioned members. We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

„Äé About Us „Äè‚Ö†
Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.
„Äé Benefits „Äè‚Ö°
[+] Assistance with clientele [+] Push for safety and security [+] Friendly environment [+] Benefits from services [+] Giveaways (Workers benefit) [+] Back-up [+] Etc.
„Äé Requirements „Äè‚Ö¢
[-] 3+ Star Horse [-] Respect, discipline and loyalty [-] Devotion to what we stand for [-] Activity on Roblox (TWW) & Discord [-] Common sense [-] Abidance to our Rules [-] Abidance to Discord TOS (Includes 13+) [-] Decent PVP Skills
„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£
We are a PMC, offering our services to anybody who needs it. You can find our shop in the Marketplace server, under the name #paid-protection. Please consider taking a look around, perhaps a service and interest you. We will try our best to reach a deal with you if you seek business, and do our best to provide commissioned members. We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

" ... Progression, Preservation, & Protection ‚Ä¶ "

„Äé About Us „Äè‚Ö†
Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.
„Äé Benefits „Äè‚Ö°
[+] Assistance with clientele [+] Push for safety and security [+] Friendly environment [+] Benefits from services [+] Giveaways (Workers benefit) [+] Back-up [+] Etc.
„Äé Requirements „Äè‚Ö¢
[-] 3+ Star Horse [-] Respect, discipline and loyalty [-] Devotion to what we stand for [-] Activity on Roblox (TWW) & Discord [-] Common sense [-] Abidance to our Rules [-] Abidance to Discord TOS (Includes 13+) [-] Decent PVP Skills
„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£
We are a PMC, offering our services to anybody who needs it. You can find our shop in the Marketplace server, under the name #paid-protection. Please consider taking a look around, perhaps a service and interest you. We will try our best to reach a deal with you if you seek business, and do our best to provide commissioned members. We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

TGMB TGMB or better known as The Green Mountain Boys was founded in late December of 2019 by Sharpsteer. „Äé About Us „Äè‚Ö†
Founded and established on the 10th of August, 2020, the Pinkerton Private Eye Agency {PPEA} operates as a PMC and private security guard company in TWW. It was founded by WackoEric and sheka335, revolving around the idea that people could use mercenaries, or assistance in general; the values and fundamental ideology of the PPEA has remained that up to this day.
„Äé Benefits „Äè‚Ö°
[+] Assistance with clientele [+] Push for safety and security [+] Friendly environment [+] Benefits from services [+] Giveaways (Workers benefit) [+] Back-up [+] Etc.
„Äé Requirements „Äè‚Ö¢
[-] 3+ Star Horse [-] Respect, discipline and loyalty [-] Devotion to what we stand for [-] Activity on Roblox (TWW) & Discord [-] Common sense [-] Abidance to our Rules [-] Abidance to Discord TOS (Includes 13+) [-] Decent PVP Skills
„Äé Details „Äè‚Ö£
We are a PMC, offering our services to anybody who needs it. You can find our shop in the Marketplace server, under the name #paid-protection. Please consider taking a look around, perhaps a service and interest you. We will try our best to reach a deal with you if you seek business, and do our best to provide commissioned members. We operate as a PMC, and were founded as that, however, we can also be considered law-enforcement. We will not provoke you intentionally unless we absolutely must. We provide security services to clients on a contractual basis.

[T.G.M.B] Fx 15-Feb-22 07:22 AM
TGMB TGMB or better known as The Green Mountain Boys was founded in late December of 2019 by Sharpsteer. We're based off of the real life militia which helped the United States gain independence back during the American revolution. We are the oldest TWW faction still out there. We know the ropes of the community. The difference between our faction and everyone else's is that we strain all toxicity and our main goal is to have fun, while still being able to be strong in battle. We host often events and raids, and we have gamenights every now and then so you can play with the members and focus on having fun. Joining the server below, you will need to apply for TGMB, if you pass the application you will be faced with a set of tryouts, although that is explained more thoroughly in the Recruitment Center. https://discord.gg/4DaUVVNs56 https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/744113129188884540/822187236032381008/0.1.tgmb.png
